<p><span class="anchor" id="p2"></span><span class="c4">[٣١٣٦ - ض ف و]</span><a href="#p2" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p3"></span>ضفَا يَضفُو، اضْفُ، ضَفْوًا وضُفُوًّا، فهو ضافٍ<a href="#p3" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p4"></span><span class="c5">• ضفا مالُه:</span> نما وكثُر <span class="c1">"ضفا الماءُ: فاض"</span> ° ضفا الحوضُ: فاض بالماء.<a href="#p4" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p5"></span><span class="c5">• ضفا الثَّوبُ:</span> طال وسَبَغَ.<a href="#p5" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p> </div>